-> Attackers can use the thc-hydra tool to gain unauthorized remote access to a target system through password cracking or password-spraying attacks

->  This tool allows attackers to use different options on how to attack with logins and passwords.

-> or example, attackers can use options such as -l for login and -p for password to instruct hydra

-> to better undertand the tool perform practical by watching this :-
